| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3310 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: feaa85c5-6d8c-5b7b-a40a-38387cbae887"
